This is the Debian GNU/Linux prepackaged version of xsysinfo.

This package was put together by Michael Meskes <meskes@debian.org>,
from sources obtained from:
sunsite.unc.edu:/pub/Linux/system/status/xstatus/xsysinfo-1.6.tar.gz

Version 1.7 is based on sources distributed with Mandrake Linux 10.2.

It is was maintained, for some time, by Hugo Haas <hugo@debian.org>.
It is now maintained by Sandro Tosi <matrixhasu@gmail.com>

